headline: T2 Biosystems Announces Plans to License its Proprietary Technology to Expand its Leadership in Direct-From-Whole-Blood Detection of Sepsis-Causing Pathogens
summary: Intends to accelerate broad adoption of direct-from-whole-blood diagnostics, generate non-dilutive capital, and create a new royalty revenue streamLEXINGTON, Mass., Dec. 09, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- T2 Biosystems, Inc. (NASDAQ: TTOO) (the “Company”), a leader in the rapid detection of sepsis-causing pathogens and antibiotic resistance genes, today announced plans to license its proprietary technology to expand its leadership in direct-from-whole-blood detection of sepsis-causing pathogens.
